// SKIP: Q&A concerns whether a named NPC stat-block action is an innate ability or a physical lootable item — a narrative/rules-interpretation question with no mechanical predicate in the spec. The spec models attack resolution, damage, conditions, and equipment AC/properties, but has no concept of "innate ability vs. carried item" for NPC actions, no item-attunement system, and no NPC stat-block representation. There is nothing to assert.